gnu.prolog.term
Class CompoundTerm

java.lang.Object
  gnu.prolog.term.Term
      gnu.prolog.term.CompoundTerm
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable
public class CompoundTerm
extends Term

Compound terms are the basic method for combining terms. In foo(a,b) foo/2 is the compound term while a and b are AtomTerms

Version:
0.0.1
